        </div>
        <div class="con">
          <div class="nlst">
            <h3>
              <div class="note-toggle rr">
                <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/28814828/" class="note-unfolder">展开</a>
                <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="note-folder">收起</a>
              </div>
              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/28814828/" class="">第18页</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/71794666/" class=" " title="珈珈">珈珈</a>
              
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="28814828">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">你从来没有想到过，世界上原来有这样一种感情，当你看着他的脸，心里完全是疼痛的。</span>
                <p class="pl">
